window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>My first crush. My first heartbreak. My brother’s best friend.</p> <p>The butterflies in my stomach turned into full blown eagles the second our lips touched. A kiss under the stars that changed our relationship forever.</p> <p>After a lifetime of wishing, I stared up into Ford’s eyes with his fingers caressing my cheek and my heart racing.</p> <p>The evening ended with my heart bleeding on the ballroom floor.</p> <p>He destroyed my heart two years ago...but now he wants back in my life.</p> <p>This time I won’t fall under his spell. I’ll resist his sexy, scruffy beard, and pantie-melting smirk.</p> <p>I thought I was over him. Hell, I fully planned to wave to him through my rearview mirror...but with one text, in the middle of the night, I know I'm in over my head.</p> <p>Ford: I need you.</p>"; 
